{"tid":1207383,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思］3點衝 點樣衝 ？","createTime":"2019-06-12T06:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T01:50:03.000Z","uid":43313,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb8178673169e9643e418990247e4f70651b6ae0","tid":1207383,"uid":43313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"今朝守龍和道，搬水馬上面咪有好多白色一塊塊板？攞嚟做盾。 係好輕但勝在數量多，同起碼有效過遮。你地擺喺水馬上面無撚用。<br />\n<br />\n後排嘅人拎塊板保護前面嘅人，如此類推。再後啲嘅人，敢扔嘅扔磚。唔敢嘅扔水樽，垃圾。前面裝備比人搶，後面即刻補。總之數量愈多愈好。<br />\n<br />\n草地班人，幫手斟水，傳物資。唔衝都好有用。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，求下你地，唔好再坐。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知work5work, 但我好想好想出一分力。"},{"pid":"db60bd9352dd9f5391661783fe7c2e7684d0bc3b","tid":1207383,"uid":156990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iMzXVUU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiMzXVUU.gif&h=794fee4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhatever it takes"},{"pid":"0573b301ceac4dfa91872d85ab9df03a357727fe","tid":1207383,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3e195748215b7e963a624e3757db14b581072f","tid":1207383,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}